Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.25,0:00:05.38,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,在那场战斗中  你就算死了也不奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.04,0:00:10.13,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,即便如此我还是让人最优先治疗你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.42,0:00:11.59,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,让你活了下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.34,0:00:14.68,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,为的是让你回答我的问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.22,0:00:19.47,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你是之前待在迪米特里耶城里的魔女吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.89,0:00:21.60,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会在那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.14,0:00:23.48,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,跟他是什么关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.02,0:00:26.35,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你的目标也是特大混沌吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.57,0:00:33.28,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子你很擅长召唤恶魔啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.70,0:00:36.95,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说召唤出恶魔领主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.07,0:00:40.83,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,引发了大圣堂惨剧的人就是你吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.62,0:00:46.67,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,在埃兰姆的中心杀害同盟和联合的盟主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.79,0:00:49.63,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你一个人怎么可能办得到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.63,0:00:53.21,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,没有组织做后盾应该是办不到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.17,0:00:55.05,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,没错吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.98,0:01:11.94,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.13,0:02:54.72,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法师协会认定将黑魔女雅娜是引发大圣堂惨剧的元凶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.85,0:02:57.18,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那边已派出使者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.43,0:03:01.02,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们立即在西斯迪纳处刑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.27,0:03:02.10,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,处刑？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.44,0:03:04.23,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,都没详细审问过就处刑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.61,0:03:06.69,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,通常来说是不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.73,0:03:11.65,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,协会究竟在想什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.66,0:03:17.33,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,为赞赏提欧•科尔内罗阁下此次的功绩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.58,0:03:19.75,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,根据协会的规定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.95,0:03:21.62,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,现赐其伯爵的爵位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.29,0:03:26.67,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,正式任命其为西斯迪纳及布鲁塔巴的领主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.84,0:03:31.13,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,协助擒获黑魔女的功绩另行奖赏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.14,0:03:39.97,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.22,0:04:20.77,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,一直都是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.27,0:04:25.52,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,大家尽情利用完我之后再把我抛弃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.94,0:04:28.82,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不会让你们得逞呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.82,0:04:31.61,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我将自己的灵魂献给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.07,0:04:33.78,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,恶魔领主莉莉丝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.37,0:04:44.66,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然能独自一人召唤恶魔领主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.68,0:05:04.06,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.56,0:05:05.85,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,大圣堂的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.94,0:05:09.27,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,惨剧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.36,0:05:14.69,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,别以为这就算完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.53,0:05:19.87,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我会在地狱等着你们掉下来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.05,0:05:41.18,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,击败罗西尼家抓住黑魔女的提欧•科尔内罗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.26,0:05:45.02,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎被魔法师协会承认为西斯迪纳的领主了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.35,0:05:47.31,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我可没把那种小角色放在眼里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.64,0:05:52.40,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,需要注意的人就只有一个塞维斯王拉席克•达维多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.57,0:05:56.53,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,可是  永夜之森的城主代理提欧•科尔内罗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.74,0:05:59.45,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,深受阿尔图克的人们爱戴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.57,0:06:04.58,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦他从罗西尼的暴政中解放了故乡西斯迪纳的消息传开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.70,0:06:09.17,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,目前独立君主们的叛乱或许会愈演愈烈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.29,0:06:09.67,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,嘁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.25,0:06:12.13,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,报告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.54,0:06:15.96,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,独立君主正在进攻我方要塞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.05,0:06:16.55,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,na'ni？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.55,0:06:25.68,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,驻守了足足一千士兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.97,0:06:28.81,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,居然连两天都撑不到这是怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.39,0:06:32.61,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎有差不多半数士兵被佯攻引得甜动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.65,0:06:34.23,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,期间遭受了袭击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.44,0:06:37.61,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,据说敌军之人还有魔女和狼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.32,0:06:40.11,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,米尔扎大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.20,0:06:40.82,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.57,0:06:43.87,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这已经不是什么叛变了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.45,0:06:49.08,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,应该视为阿尔图克的领民变成士兵攻打过来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.37,0:06:50.87,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这我还是知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.37,0:06:54.96,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,可为何人们不顺从我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.21,0:06:56.92,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我无非是遵守爵位制度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.96,0:06:59.59,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,准备进行正当的统治
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.84,0:07:01.22,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,所言极是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.76,0:07:04.35,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,领民必须顺从领主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.55,0:07:07.77,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,如果协助了领主之外的君主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.85,0:07:09.56,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那就等于是敌人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.89,0:07:12.56,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你的意思是让我杀了领民吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.73,0:07:16.69,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,在下认为这也是无奈之举
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.61,0:07:21.45,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这确实会致使无辜的领民死亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.74,0:07:27.74,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,可是责任在拿他们作掩护反抗我们的那些人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.04,0:07:30.83,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,还请下定决心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.62,0:07:32.75,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,决心啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.08,0:07:36.13,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我就接受你的献策好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.38,0:07:38.71,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过要进攻哪里我说了算
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.96,0:07:39.42,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.96,0:07:41.47,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,首先是白魔女的村落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.88,0:07:43.51,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来是狼人的村落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.01,0:07:47.18,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,然后是袭击这要塞的独立君主们的据点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.56,0:07:51.35,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,让阿尔图克的人民见识一下我的决心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.65,0:08:02.61,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这边 快点快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.99,0:08:03.78,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,抓紧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.78,0:08:05.07,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,快进去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.34,0:08:24.47,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我过去对维拉尔的人民太过尊重了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.84,0:08:28.14,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,今后就可以毫无顾忌地进攻莱加里亚了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.93,0:08:31.77,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,但愿不会有变数吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.93,0:08:33.98,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,事态进展都跟你预期的一样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.02,0:08:35.35,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你究竟还有什么好担心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.98,0:08:39.48,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是提欧・科尔内罗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.86,0:08:43.49,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我担心他会回到阿尔图克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.99,0:08:45.20,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,区区提欧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.78,0:08:48.95,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,到头来  他在西斯迪纳还是煽动民众
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.99,0:08:50.49,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,害得他们付出牺牲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.58,0:08:52.75,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,最后恬不知耻地以英雄自居
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.87,0:08:56.25,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,恕我直言也许这才是王道吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.54,0:08:57.67,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,可笑至极
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.04,0:09:00.88,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过经过你这次献策
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.05,0:09:04.34,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我切身体会到自己的觉悟还不够
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.55,0:09:08.43,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,从今往后  我会杀光阻碍我前进的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.68,0:09:11.31,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,无论我走的是怎样一条路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.18,0:09:15.10,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我都绝不会停步回头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.31,0:09:22.02,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,今后该怎么办呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.32,0:09:25.07,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,估计村落主全烧毁了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.37,0:09:30.91,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,提欧・科尔内罗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.33,0:09:33.54,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子要回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.54,0:09:38.21,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,有报告称在米尔扎太子的指示下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.33,0:09:41.17,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,狼人白魔女的村落被烧毁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.29,0:09:45.88,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不顺从的领民被肃清了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.38,0:09:48.43,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,必须抓紧了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.43,0:09:53.14,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我之前就想过继罗西尼家之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.39,0:09:54.97,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,下一个战争对象就是米尔扎了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.22,0:09:56.48,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,他是个难缠的对手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.14,0:09:59.27,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  只要没打倒他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.85,0:10:01.44,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,条约就不会有未来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.82,0:10:09.41,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,回来得好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.16,0:10:12.33,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.83,0:10:14.58,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,平定西斯迪纳真是精彩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.33,0:10:16.45,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,劳拉前辈？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.50,0:10:19.54,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我听说你自杀了来着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.04,0:10:21.79,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏了海尔格的毒药
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.13,0:10:23.71,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我没死成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.92,0:10:28.84,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在侍奉的是艾德吉雅大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.22,0:10:35.39,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,提欧我打算在本次会议中提出从属的请求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.89,0:10:38.93,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,能不能再等一段时间呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.10,0:10:41.27,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,真是让人着急啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.56,0:10:45.48,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟你我的立场跟最初战斗时不一样了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.82,0:10:47.32,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,爵位一升上去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.61,0:10:49.40,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,增加的净是麻烦事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.90,0:10:50.95,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,一点没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.83,0:11:00.00,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,莫雷诺前辈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.21,0:11:00.87,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.79,0:11:05.88,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,此次的会议 能让我来主持吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.13,0:11:08.92,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你又不是盟主的魔法师要是由你来主持
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.09,0:11:12.13,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,等于是宣称盟主换人了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.55,0:11:17.31,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟拉席克大人会提出从属请求嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.18,0:11:22.81,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,于是相对的你想表现出同意从属的意向啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.44,0:11:24.86,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.11,0:11:26.98,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛  你就小心行事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.07,0:11:30.44,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟还有很多君主对提欧大人不怀好意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.82,0:11:35.49,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,要是有人追究你们外出期间有很多人丧命的责任…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.20,0:11:38.24,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,明白  我会当心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.87,0:11:44.79,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来将举行阿尔图克条约君主会议
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.59,0:11:47.21,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,西露卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.55,0:11:47.92,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.42,0:11:51.55,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,在开会之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.38,0:11:59.31,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我想先为我前往西斯迪纳期间死亡的众多阿尔图克君主默哀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.45,0:12:14.20,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.37,0:12:16.95,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那么…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.99,0:12:20.83,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,提欧阁下在西斯迪纳的活跃表现确实很精彩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.04,0:12:22.37,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过正因如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.58,0:12:26.04,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不免让人觉得阁下更该留在大陆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.13,0:12:28.09,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这恐怕值得商榷吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.09,0:12:30.88,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,如果说外出的提欧阁下有责任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.01,0:12:35.59,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那留守的我们责任就更大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.63,0:12:37.89,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是在追究责任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.05,0:12:42.77,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想说  英雄提欧阁下外出造成的影响究竟有多大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.93,0:12:45.94,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,可是  身为属于条约的君主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.98,0:12:47.65,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,比起与同盟的战争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.86,0:12:52.40,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,居然优先解放故乡这不妥吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.28,0:12:59.07,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,比起责任现在更该讨论条约的未来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.49,0:13:05.00,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过  阿尔弗雷德阁下似乎很关心谁会当上盟主啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.83,0:13:08.92,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,艾德吉雅阁下有什么意见吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.13,0:13:14.59,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望能由拉席克阁下继续指挥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.97,0:13:20.93,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,目前我的哈曼不断受到驻扎进斯达尔克的诺尔德军进攻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.64,0:13:25.48,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我依靠给他们财物阻止了进攻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.85,0:13:28.15,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过佶计国库很快就会耗空吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.44,0:13:34.86,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,在此之前  首先应该强化以拉席克为盟主的现状
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.24,0:13:37.95,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,并对抗米尔扎才对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.24,0:13:39.07,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.70,0:13:42.16,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你说的很对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.79,0:13:47.12,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我也认为现在确实不该更换盟主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.21,0:13:47.58,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.00,0:13:51.59,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 就像阿尔弗雷麻阁下刚才说的一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.75,0:13:55.46,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,君主们死亡的责任在我身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.80,0:13:57.38,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,居然承认了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.18,0:14:00.14,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,因此我想在此发誓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.18,0:14:02.10,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我要进攻阿尔图克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.68,0:14:06.81,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,讨伐达尔塔尼亚太子米尔扎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.19,0:14:13.73,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,当然我一个人是办不到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.19,0:14:16.03,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我还想借助大家的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.40,0:14:19.45,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,提欧阁下会冲锋陷阵讨伐米尔扎太子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.66,0:14:22.32,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,夺回阿尔图克是这样吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.49,0:14:28.79,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,前提是能获得维拉尔阁下的弟弟赛尔杰阁下的认可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.29,0:14:31.33,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,凭我是没法战胜米尔扎的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.54,0:14:33.17,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是很清楚的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.25,0:14:34.71,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,居然承认了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.67,0:14:37.38,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,理由当然不止这一个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.47,0:14:40.43,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,既然赛尔杰阁下没有异议
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.55,0:14:42.18,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那大家就没意见了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.19,0:14:55.40,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,话说  提欧阁下有自信战胜那个米尔扎吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.90,0:14:57.19,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我才没自信呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.94,0:15:00.95,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  若是不打倒米尔扎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.03,0:15:02.53,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,条约就不会有未来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.28,0:15:06.16,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,打倒他也能主成维拉尔阁下的遗志
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.88,0:15:19.76,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,久违地试着烤了点心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.47,0:15:22.30,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,但愿合口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.44,0:15:35.36,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  首先是阿尔图克的平定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.44,0:15:36.44,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,真是精彩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.11,0:15:39.36,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,花费的时间超乎预计
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.49,0:15:40.53,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,真是惭愧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.36,0:15:44.99,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不知道阿尔图克重要性的人会说闲话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.28,0:15:47.03,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过若是换成别人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.16,0:15:50.00,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕已经从那里逃回来了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.08,0:15:53.71,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,谁统治跟人民又没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.75,0:15:55.21,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能视领主不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.38,0:15:58.09,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,有时也会被当成奴隶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.75,0:16:01.97,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,被当成反倒容易死心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.05,0:16:04.84,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,给人民不彻底的自由才会让他们反抗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.97,0:16:09.52,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我听说斯达尔克的奴隶造反了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.23,0:16:13.56,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我虽然是同盟的盟主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.64,0:16:17.27,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,但不会干预诸国的统治方针
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.56,0:16:21.53,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我也不希望统治不安定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.90,0:16:25.86,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,更别说以此为由拒绝协助同盟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.12,0:16:34.62,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你就多花些时间慢慢整治混乱吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.29,0:16:39.04,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,在此期间  我会攻下莱加里亚和哈曼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.34,0:16:41.59,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,哈曼是我的猎物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.88,0:16:44.93,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我打算我方与卢克莱尔伯爵的战斗结束后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.63,0:16:48.89,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,也从布鲁塔巴进攻奥赛尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.18,0:16:50.60,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.02,0:16:56.40,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,诺尔德公几乎已经拿下北方的小大陆布莱特兰德了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.73,0:16:58.86,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就保持这势头直接进攻联合吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.27,0:17:01.28,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不够团结的联合诸国
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.44,0:17:03.40,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,根本不是埃里克阁下的对手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.57,0:17:07.61,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过让人在意的是提欧•科尔内罗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.91,0:17:10.91,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那男人的目标应该是解放阿尔图克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.70,0:17:13.75,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,早晚会决一胜负吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.16,0:17:16.17,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,联合的动员力不可小看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.54,0:17:19.79,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,有需要的话希望你不要有所顾忌直接申请援军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.09,0:17:22.09,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,还有乌尔莉卡阁下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.34,0:17:25.55,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,无论斯达尔克处于怎样的状况你都要派出援军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.38,0:17:27.97,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.22,0:17:33.64,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我们三人齐心合力击败阿尔图克条约
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.77,0:17:36.44,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,比起一个人吃点心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.98,0:17:39.69,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,还是像这样聚集起来吃更美味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.87,0:17:51.45,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,进来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.37,0:17:56.87,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.37,0:18:01.96,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才提欧•科尔内罗宣布要夺回永夜之森
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.55,0:18:07.09,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我就先加紧赶回阿尔图克了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.13,0:18:10.05,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,米尔扎阁下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.47,0:18:16.81,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,千万不可错误估计提欧•科尔內罗的实力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.73,0:18:18.69,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.06,0:18:25.03,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望我们能在这片森林迎击米尔扎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.28,0:18:27.74,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我要以此地为跳板讨伐米尔扎太子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.95,0:18:29.49,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,夺回阿尔图克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.95,0:18:37.45,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,达尔塔尼亚全军有一万人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.70,0:18:39.96,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,而我军只有两干人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.25,0:18:41.33,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,如果正面冲突
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.38,0:18:42.54,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我们毫无胜算
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.88,0:18:45.80,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  我军有地利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.38,0:18:48.38,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,拥有庞大军队的达尔塔尼亚军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.55,0:18:52.64,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,在树木繁茂的永夜之森是无法自由行动的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.85,0:18:56.14,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还无法发挥出机动力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.93,0:18:58.77,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,只要在永夜之森战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.85,0:19:00.60,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就一定能赢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.98,0:19:02.86,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,问题反倒在后面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.48,0:19:07.86,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我们早晚得离开森林去进攻独角兽城
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.44,0:19:11.95,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,可是想攻陷防御坚固的独角兽城
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.11,0:19:13.82,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就得具备几个条件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.37,0:19:16.08,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,首先是士兵吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.12,0:19:20.75,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉有必要集结阿尔图克条约的所有兵力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.87,0:19:21.42,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.67,0:19:23.38,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,总之要尽可能多动员士兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.46,0:19:27.17,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,最好把达尔塔尼亚军限制在城内
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.55,0:19:30.84,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,盟主拉席克为了集结条约的全部兵力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.13,0:19:32.47,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,也已经开始行动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.89,0:19:35.80,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,另一个问题是敌人的援军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.26,0:19:39.81,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,所幸  瓦尔林德军由于要跟卢克莱尔战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.06,0:19:42.23,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,无法派出大军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.31,0:19:44.48,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,其他有可能派出援军的地方呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.94,0:19:47.02,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,达尔塔尼亚本国和斯达尔克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.44,0:19:51.70,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,达尔塔尼亚方面似乎反米尔扎势力已经集结起来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.82,0:19:54.53,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,目前正在请求他们的帮助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.70,0:19:58.20,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,斯达尔克那边听说奴隶正在造反
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.70,0:19:59.70,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,听说是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.20,0:20:01.00,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.16,0:20:03.00,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,利用这一点如何呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.25,0:20:05.21,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想利用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.08,0:20:07.75,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,可是该派谁去呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.21,0:20:09.13,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,让我去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.46,0:20:09.80,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.13,0:20:14.01,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我们罗西尼家在西斯迪纳一直实行暴政
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.22,0:20:17.51,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道该如何防止领民叛乱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.01,0:20:20.10,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,当然 反过来也一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.06,0:20:23.39,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,能拜托你吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.14,0:20:25.27,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,请交给我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.81,0:20:31.07,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才已经说过我们所处的状况了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.74,0:20:33.53,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不知道会在哪里受阻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.74,0:20:35.57,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦变成那样就会一蹶不振
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.86,0:20:39.08,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这等于是踩在薄冰上过河
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.79,0:20:42.04,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我们只能走到底
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.46,0:20:48.54,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,提欧•科尔内罗似乎宣布要杀死太子夺回阿尔图克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.09,0:20:51.80,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,夺走永夜之森应该是开端
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.88,0:20:52.63,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,夺走？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.05,0:20:54.84,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,偷偷摸摸地跑回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.88,0:20:57.51,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,还真敢说是从我这夺走的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.68,0:20:59.18,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,您说的沒错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.35,0:21:01.35,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过恕我直言 在阿尔图克伯爵维披尔死亡后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.43,0:21:05.02,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,永夜之森就是米尔扎大人领地了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.06,0:21:08.65,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,区区提欧 不堪一击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.77,0:21:09.90,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,准备出击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.98,0:21:11.02,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,请稍等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.57,0:21:13.36,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.99,0:21:15.57,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,攻进去太危险了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.95,0:21:17.86,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,应该等他们从森林出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.24,0:21:20.83,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得我会输给区区提欧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.62,0:21:24.58,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,在永夜之森之外的地方肯定不会输吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.08,0:21:26.79,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,但是在那个魔境战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.00,0:21:29.25,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,对我军而言压倒性的不利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.67,0:21:33.96,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,而且提欧・科尔内罗比太子想象中厉害不可轻敌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.01,0:21:34.55,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,住嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.59,0:21:41.22,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经说出意见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.31,0:21:44.22,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,做决定的是太子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.47,0:21:45.98,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经下过命令了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.35,0:21:49.10,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,进攻永夜之森杀死提欧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.73,0:21:51.36,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,立刻开始准备
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.07,0:21:53.65,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,垃命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.28,0:21:56.90,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,该死的提欧•科尔内罗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.45,0:22:00.99,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我要让你为挑战我感到后悔
